title: Tory MP Kwarsi Kwarteng caught laughing during tax credit debate in House of Commons
text: A Conservative MP has been condemned for his behaviour in the House of Commons after he was caught laughing out loud during the debate over the Chancellor’s package of £4.4bn cuts to tax credits. Read more
